data.description: Come see this 4/2 well-maintained home in Coastal Woods. Featuring vinyl plank flooring, granite countertops, farm house lighting, and brick pavers for increased parking space. Relax on you back screened in porch while watching the wild life by the lake. Centrally located, you can be at beautiful New Smyrna Beach in 10 mins, shopping on Canal St. in 5 mins, or to Orlando/Disney in 45 mins. This house stayed high and dry during the hurricanes. This is a must see!
